title: Hi! I'm new here in OCE (Originally from Philippines server) Looking for non toxic players to play
body: Hi! I'm Graves Bot {{champion:104}}  and I've been playing league since 2011. IGNS Are: Udyr (Plat IV) {{champion:77}}  , Olaf (Gold IV) {{champion:2}}  , Jayce Bot (Gold V) {{champion:126}} and A Smurf Account (Gold III) {{item:3113}}  .  I also have a level 35 account here in OCE Ign is Pyke Tyson {{champion:555}}  . Anyone want to play for fun? looking for non toxic players to play with <3 I'm new here in OCE server. Add me!
